data.title: EVA LONGORIA AND TONY PARKER
data.meta_description: The couple shares their wedding only with OK! The dress! The wedding party! The ceremony! The reception! Only OK! was on hand to see Eva Longoria and Tony Parker celebrate their love in the most romantic city in the world. More than 200 guests watched the Desperate Housewives star make her way down…
